 * basic command

  # docker volume create = To create docker volume
  # docker volume ls = To check list created volume
  # docker volume inspect volume-name = To check , where is connect your volume
  # /var/lib/docker/volumes/my-volume/
  # docker run -d --name container-name -v volume-name:/files port-image = To run volume , To create a container
  # docker exec -it container-name bash = To open container
  # docker volume rm volume-name = To remove volume 
  # docker volume prune = To remove all not use volume


